The paper proposes a new approach for nested entity mention detection, which is a task in natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The proposed approach involves modeling and leveraging phrase structures, which suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions an objective function and experiments, which are common in the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
